########### Self-Healing Demo #######

@@ Delete a Pod:
[root@k8s-control01 ~]# kubectl delete pod nginx-rs-x1abc

@@ Watch:
[root@k8s-control01 ~]# kubectl get pods -w

@@ Observe:
Old Pod Terminating
New Pod Created
Desired Count Maintained
Assignment
Delete all Pods one by one.

@@ Observe:
ReplicaSet keeps recreating them.

@@ Question:
Can users still access the application?

@@ Answer:
Yes (if Service is configured properly).

