######### Banking Application HA #############
@@ Requirement:
99.99% Availability

@@ Design:
ReplicaSet: 3

Worker-1
Worker-2
Worker-3

One Pod per worker.

@@ Benefits:
Pod Failure -> Survives
Node Failure -> Survives
OS Reboot -> Survives

